19½Ã 19:14 Let the words of my mouth and the meditation of my heart Be acceptable in Thy sight, O LORD, my rock and my Redeemer.
19½Ã 20:1 {For the choir director. A Psalm of David.} May the LORD answer you in the day of trouble! May the name of the God of Jacob set you [securely] on high!
19½Ã 20:2 May He send you help from the sanctuary, And support you from Zion!
