19½Ã 45:8 All Thy garments are [fragrant with] myrrh and aloes [and] cassia; Out of ivory palaces stringed instruments have made Thee glad.
19½Ã 45:9 Kings' daughters are among Thy noble ladies; At Thy right hand stands the queen in gold from Ophir.
