19½Ã 51:1 {For the choir director. A Psalm of David, when Nathan the prophet came to him,} (after he had gone in to Bathsheba.) Be gracious to me, O God, according to Thy lovingkindness; According to the greatness of Thy compassion blot out my transgressions.
