19½Ã 83:17 Let them be ashamed and dismayed forever; And let them be humiliated and perish,
19½Ã 83:18 That they may know that Thou alone, whose name is the LORD, Art the Most High over all the earth.
19½Ã 84:1 {For the choir director; on the Gittith. A Psalm of the sons of Korah.} How lovely are Thy dwelling places, O LORD of hosts!
