19½Ã 88:5 Forsaken among the dead, Like the slain who lie in the grave, Whom Thou dost remember no more, And they are cut off from Thy hand.
19½Ã 88:6 Thou hast put me in the lowest pit, In dark places, in the depths.
19½Ã 88:7 Thy wrath has rested upon me, And Thou hast afflicted me with all Thy waves. Selah.
