19½Ã 88:16 Thy burning anger has passed over me; Thy terrors have destroyed me.
19½Ã 88:17 They have surrounded me like water all day long; They have encompassed me altogether.
19½Ã 88:18 Thou hast removed lover and friend far from me; My acquaintances are [in] darkness.
19½Ã 89:1 {A Maskil of Ethan the Ezrahite.} I will sing of the lovingkindness of the LORD forever; To all generations I will make known Thy faithfulness with my mouth.
